WEBVTT

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:32.040
but these were unwinnable wars.

00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:37.336
We became the very instrument
through which more deaths occurred,

00:12:37.360 --> 00:12:41.096
complicit in causing further misery

00:12:41.120 --> 00:12:43.720
for the selfish benefit of the cruel few.

00:12:52.280 --> 00:12:53.496
So over time,

00:12:53.520 --> 00:12:54.720
a very long time,

00:12:56.600 --> 00:12:57.800
I opened my eyes.

00:12:59.960 --> 00:13:01.440
I began to dare